# List tags of a image
```sh
skopeo list-tags docker://[<host>/][<path>/]<image>
```

For offcial docker images, the host and path can be omitted.
```sh
skopeo list-tags docker://golang
# is equivalent to
skopeo list-tags docker://docker.io/library/golang
```

For non-offcial images, the host can be omitted but path must be specified.
```sh
skopeo list-tags docker://codercom/code-server
```

For other registry, the host must be specified. If the registry is code repository like GitHub Container Registry, the path is usually `<repo>/<owner>`.
```sh
skopeo list-tags docker://ghcr.io/helmfile/helmfile
```

Private registry is also supported.
```sh
skopeo list-tags docker://myregistry.com/path/to/myimage
```
